mixin type-sections
    .type-sections
        .type-sections__item
            h1(class="type-sections__h1-caption") H1
            p(class="type-sections__h1-description") This one is the sub-section or widget title
        .type-sections__item
            h2(class="type-sections__h2-caption") H2
            p(class="type-sections__h2-description") Next one is the item title inside widgets 
        .type-sections__item
            h3(class="type-sections__h3-caption") H3
            p(class="type-sections__h3-description") This is a label or CTA text
        .type-sections__item
            p(class="type-sections__body-caption") Body
            p(class="type-sections__body-description") This is the body text which is used for most of the design, like paragraphs, lists, etc.